make_namer[source]

make_namer(prefix='g')

Creates a dictionary that generates short names (suitable for regex groups) given arbitrary inputs.

{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
namer = make_namer()
assert namer['hello.world'] == 'g1'
assert namer['hi.there'] == 'g2'
assert namer['hello.world'] == 'g1'
